STATE
v.
Delton MAYNOR. No. 241P11-5. Supreme Court of North Carolina. April 13, 2016. Kimberly N. Callahan, Assistant Attorney General, for State of N.C. Delton Maynor, Smithfield, for Maynor, Delton. Todd Williams, District Attorney, for State of N.C.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 4th of March 2016 by Defendant for Petition for Discretionary Review of Writ of Certiorari:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 13th of April 2016."
